  "text": "By means of the differential operators presented in [CITATION_1] , we can calculate the infinitesimals ζ ;... as functionals of the infinitesimals ξ y(z)dz , ξ x , ξ t , η φ or, using the relation Equation (21), infinitesimals of ξ γ(z) , ξ x , ξ t , η φ . For the viscous Hopf-Burgers functional differential equation (FDE), we need the three infinitesimals ζ ;t , ζ ;xy(x)y(x) and ζ ;xxy(x) .",
